OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying very
OL,6,Fwarm into the evening with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine. A very warm and muggy night
OL,8,Fto follow, with difficult sleeping
OL,9,Fconditions. Perhaps with a few mist
OL,10,Fand fog patches.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FExtreme heat warnings in
OL,13,Fplace. Very hot and humid with strong
OL,14,Fsunshine through the day. Light winds
OL,15,Fand continuing to feel very warm and
OL,16,Fmuggy into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
