OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FExtremely hot and humid on Thursday,
OL,7,Fparticularly in the south. Strong
OL,8,Fsunshine, but with the increasing risk
OL,9,Fof thunderstorms from Thursday evening
OL,10,Fonwards. Becoming slightly cooler from
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
